    "Developing research questions: the first step focuses on formulating research questions that will guide the systematic literature review.",
    "This is done with a particular emphasis on the research objective, which is to determine the dimensions of research related to CEXs and DEXs.",
    "Therefore, the following questions are specified:",
    "is the current understanding of CEXs and DEXs in the literature?",
    "Is there a common definition or does the understanding vary widely?"
  ]
